Author: forestdark
Text: Thank you. Right now it honestly feels as if I'm going to be stuck in this mindspace forever, but I know my brain is lying. Hugs.

Author: liquid_nitrogenn
Text: Sending love to you - I've had those days too and while I know nothing I can say will magically turn around how you're feeling, know that tomorrow is a new, fresh day, and you can make it better. (((hugs)))
